Hurdle model?

\(Y\) = log-transformed catch per unit effort

\(Z\) = indicator variable: \(1\) for \(Y > 0\), \(0\) for \(Y = 0\)

\(E(Y) = Pr(Z = 1) E(Y | Z = 1)\)

\(E(Y) = \pi \mu\)

Then model \(\pi\) with logistic regression

And model \(\mu\) with linear model
